{"tid":1691052,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"刀手頻繁出沒，出門一定要袋定帽同口罩","createTime":"2019-11-03T13:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T15:29:06.000Z","uid":108502,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf1402f2c820bb8ad2e6faa300cfe0d4c290dcf","tid":1691052,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"今時今日隨時都會有支那人／廢老周街打人<br />\n連口罩都冇個真係唔方便做嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無論何時何地，出門一定要袋定帽同口罩（甚至手套）<br />\n隨時見到有衝突就笠起救人</span><br />\n宜家除咗我哋自己之外，冇人再會保護香港人<br />\n我哋唯有提高警覺，互相保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fb2e956781743dad3f8de6672300771bc49385","tid":1691052,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1fdf3b05b8ab9f2de2dc7e6acfdfa8f293f5a03","tid":1691052,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3cc1a9670f2f9397929c1972da36595c74e3b97","tid":1691052,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c700565628157ca270e7ebe6b945b33d6433e26","tid":1691052,"uid":38164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">菠蘿蓋腳眼骨斷手指骨<br />\n取眼割耳割嘴肉剃眉肉<br />\n<br />\n香港人！還拖！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n私了藍絲一定要係五官留下不可逆轉創傷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691018\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691018</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a36d197f010db064791d6953693c946b1c06172","tid":1691052,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"a68db967fe53fc8451509086a87779db4e8a4d12","tid":1691052,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"7599e749808420